      <rules>
        <rule name="Nurgling Infestation" id="755d-4191-d174-c4de" hidden="false">
          <description>At the beginning of any turn in which Ku&apos;gath is on the table (not including the one when he arrives from Reserve), the player may roll a dice. On a roll of 4+, a new unit consisting of a single base of Nurglings enters the game by Deep Strike within 12&quot; of Ku&apos;gath.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
