        <rule name="Oracle of Eternity" id="0b26-33a9-7cae-bd18" hidden="false">
          <description>Fateweaver and all friendly units within 6&quot; may re-roll all failed Armour, invulnerable, and Cover Saves. However, for every unsaved wound suffered by Fateweaver, take a Leadership test. If the test is failed, he retreats in shock and is removed as a casualty.</description>
