              </profiles>
              <costs>
                <cost name="Points" typeId="4deb-313d-6685-f48b" value="5"/>
              </costs>
              <rules>
                <rule name="Glamour of Tzeentch" id="3084-3bd6-e9ed-1e1e" hidden="false">
                  <description>This power can be used in the enemy Shooting phase. Pick an enemy unit that is visible to the Changeling and is about to fire. If the unit is found to be within 24&quot; of the Changeling, it is affected by his mind-altering mirage.
The unit may choose to hold its fire and just stand around confused, or continue with shooting. If it opens fire they must take a Leadership test (Vehicles count as Ld 10). If the test is passed, the unit sees through the Glamour and may fire as normal.
If the test is failed, the unit must immediately fire all of its weapons against a friendly unit chosen by the Changeling among any of the enemies he can see. If the Changeling cannot see a second enemy unit, the enemy which failed will simply stand around confused as described above.</description>
                </rule>
              </rules>
            </selectionEntry>
          </selectionEntries>
          <profiles>
            <profile name="Pink Horror" typeId="556e697423232344415441232323" typeName="Unit" hidden="false" id="1688-bd53-6ebe-bf60">
